        <span class="text-4xl flex-shrink-0">‚ö†Ô∏è</span>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-light mb-2">
            Important Note for Console Players
          </h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted">
            Xbox, PlayStation, and Nintendo Switch players: Please read this section carefully!
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-secondary-dark rounded-xl p-6 mb-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-light mb-3">Console Limitation</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted mb-4">
          Unfortunately, Microsoft restricts custom server connections on console versions of Minecraft Bedrock Edition.
